Package fi.tuni.swdesign.group3.gui.view

Class DataVisualizer

java.lang.Object
fi.tuni.swdesign.group3.gui.view.DataVisualizer
Direct Known Subclasses:
RoadDataVisualizer, WeatherDataVisualizer
public abstract class DataVisualizer extends Object
An abstract base class for visualizing data using charts and tables.
Author:
Lauri Puoskari
